ZH: 我们去野外露营的时候，要记得带上蚊帐。
EN: We need to remember to bring a mosquito net when we go camping in the wild.

ZH: 妈妈在孩子的床上悬挂了蚊帐，以防蚊子叮咬。
EN: Mom hung a mosquito net over her child's bed to prevent mosquito bites.

ZH: 在热带地区旅行时，蚊帐是非常必要的。
EN: Mosquito nets are essential when traveling in tropical regions.

ZH: 家里的蚊帐已经布满了洞，需要换新的了。
EN: The mosquito net at home is full of holes and needs to be replaced.

ZH: 打开蚊帐后，可以闷得不舒服。
EN: It can be stuffy after opening the mosquito net.

ZH: 她在蚊帐内熟睡了一整夜。
EN: She slept soundly all night inside the mosquito net.

ZH: 这款蚊帐可以轻松地折叠并放入包内携带。
EN: This mosquito net can be easily folded and carried in a bag.

ZH: 孩子把蚊帐弄得满是脏污。
EN: The child made the mosquito net dirty.

ZH: 在夏天的晚上，躺在蚊帐下是最舒适的。
EN: Lying under the mosquito net on a summer night is the most comfortable.

ZH: 她对蚊子过敏，所以睡觉时必须在蚊帐内。
EN: She is allergic to mosquitoes, so she must sleep inside a mosquito net.

ZH: 南美洲的丛林里，一定要准备好蚊帐。
EN: In the jungles of South America, be sure to have a mosquito net ready.

ZH: 这款蚊帐可以有效阻挡蚊子和其他昆虫。
EN: This mosquito net can effectively block mosquitoes and other insects.

ZH: 夜晚睡觉时，每个人都应该遮上蚊帐。
EN: Everyone should cover themselves with a mosquito net when sleeping at night.

ZH: 他忘记关闭蚊帐，整晚都被蚊子叮咬。
EN: He forgot to close the mosquito net and was bitten by mosquitoes all night.

ZH: 她在亚马逊河上的帐篷内安装了蚊帐。
EN: She installed a mosquito net inside her tent on the Amazon River.

ZH: 蚊帐是非常有用的装备，可以保护我们的健康。
EN: Mosquito nets are very useful equipment that can protect our health.

ZH: 我们需要一把好的蚊香和蚊帐来防止蚊子的叮咬。
EN: We need a good mosquito repellent and mosquito net to prevent mosquito bites.

ZH: 在非洲旅行时，要特别注意使用蚊帐来防止疟疾。
EN: When traveling in Africa, be sure to use mosquito nets to prevent malaria.

ZH: 在沙漠地区露营，也要准备好蚊帐来避免叮咬。
EN: When camping in desert areas, also be prepared with mosquito nets to avoid bites.
